objects = [
    "Big Red Metallic Sphere",
    "Big Brown Matte Thing",
    "Small Blue Plastic Cube",
    "Medium Green Wooden Cylinder",
    "Big Yellow Glass Pyramid"
]

# Subtract objects that are 'Big Red Metallic Sphere' and 'Big Brown Matte Thing'
objects_to_subtract = ["Big Red Metallic Sphere", "Big Brown Matte Thing"]
remaining_objects = [obj for obj in objects if obj not in objects_to_subtract]

# Count remaining objects
remaining_count = len(remaining_objects)
remaining_count
